{"tid":1545424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"831太子站死去烈士厲鬼索命(幫手推)","createTime":"2019-09-06T01:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T04:53:28.000Z","uid":38929,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6087361b68459e2357022038dfcc66146afafb56","tid":1545424,"uid":38929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:57:34.000Z","msg":"如果831太子站真係有手足被打死，咁無論啲Popo幾無人性，殺咗人，始終會心虛，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">嚟緊星期六，聽日，就係頭七</span></span></strong>，中國人傳聞，死去的人，會係個日回魂。<br />\n<br />\n如果係冤死，被害死，更可能會開始報仇<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冤報冤，有仇報仇</span></span></span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n咁<br />\n<br />\n啲殺人黑警，心理上會承受著陰影。如果，社會上不停流傳，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">厲鬼索命</span></span></strong>。佢地心理壓力會更加重。<br />\n<br />\n到時，<br />\n<br />\n如果流出有黑警自殺，或癡咗綫(雖然佢地已經係) 等，可能就從旁佐証到的確有手足已成<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">烈士</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n黑警殺人<br />\n怨鬼纏身<br />\n午夜夢迴<br />\n厲鬼索命<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警！還眼！填命！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"291c058f3bf71002e9be052b70652873ab1bf685","tid":1545424,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:04:18.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62392aa441db59956e8